<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MindVault | The AI-Powered Notepad</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>

<nav class="navbar">
    <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-brain gradient-text"></i> MindVault</h2>
    <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/login">Login</a>
        <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
    </div>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-left">
        <h1>Think smarter.<br>Write <span class="gradient-text">faster</span>.</h1>
        <p>MindVault is an AI-integrated knowledge workspace that helps you capture ideas, organize thoughts, and generate insights at the speed of thought.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary">Start for free <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right" style="margin-left: 8px;"></i></a>
            <a href="/about" class="btn btn-outline">See how it works</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-right">
        <div class="ai-sparkle">✨</div>
        <div class="hero-mockup">
            <div class="hero-mockup-header">
                <div class="mockup-dot"></div>
                <div class="mockup-dot"></div>
                <div class="mockup-dot"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="mockup-content">
                <h3 style="margin-bottom: 15px; font-family: var(--font-display);">Project Ideas 💡</h3>
                <div class="mockup-line w-full"></div>
                <div class="mockup-line w-full"></div>
                <div class="mockup-line w-3-4"></div>
                
                <div style="margin-top: 25px; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; background: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.3);">
                    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: var(--accent-purple); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px;">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-wand-magic-sparkles"></i> AI Suggestion
                    </div>
                    <div class="mockup-line w-full"></div>
                    <div class="mockup-line w-1-2"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="features">
    <h2>Supercharge your workflow</h2>
    
    <div class="feature-grid">
        <div class="feature-card glass-panel">
            <div class="feature-icon">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-bolt gradient-text"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Instant Capture</h3>
            <p>Jot down ideas instantly. Our distraction-free editor ensures your flow state is never interrupted.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card glass-panel">
            <div class="feature-icon">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-wand-magic-sparkles gradient-text"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>AI Assistant</h3>
            <p>Summarize long notes, generate outlines, and brainstorm ideas with our built-in AI intelligence.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card glass-panel">
            <div class="feature-icon">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass gradient-text"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Semantic Search</h3>
            <p>Find what you're looking for instantly. Never lose a thought in the vault again.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card glass-panel">
            <div class="feature-icon">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-lock gradient-text"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Secure Vault</h3>
            <p>Your data is encrypted and securely stored. Your knowledge remains yours and yours alone.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<footer>
    <p>© 2026 MindVault | The AI Notepad</p>
</footer>

<script src="/theme.js"></script>
</body>
</html>